title: DDFP 463: 2-Pt Conversion Debate, Vegas Team Nicknames & Movie Talk with Bald Bryan
itunes:title: DDFP 463: 2-Pt Conversion Debate, Vegas Team Nicknames & Movie Talk with Bald Bryan
description:
Shek is joined in Studio 66 by Handsome Hank & “Bald” Bryan Bishop of the Adam Carolla Show.  The guys discuss the NBA finals, whether your kid should cheer for the local team or your favorite team, and then compete in another round of “Shek’s surprise game show.”  Plus, Bryan goes through a thorough list of actor redundancies.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
